IMPORTANT: RESUME FILE PLACEHOLDER

Please replace this file with your actual resume in PDF format.

Instructions:
1. Delete this "resume.pdf" file (or overwrite it)
2. Add your actual resume PDF
3. Make sure it's named exactly: resume.pdf
4. Place it in the same directory as index.html

The download button in your portfolio will automatically link to this file.

If you want to use a different filename:
- Open index.html
- Find: href="resume.pdf"
- Change it to your resume filename

Example: href="Anuj_Ahirwar_Resume.pdf"
